                     <interp inst="t18280911-375-person2028" type="gender" value="male"></interp>
                  </persName>
            . I am a broker. I bought a bedstead and stove of Brooks; he said he was going to harness-work, and wanted to sell them - I gave him 5s. and a pint of porter for them.</p>
               <p>
            
                  <persName id="t18280911-375-person2029">
                  THOMAS 
                  HARRISON
               <interp inst="t18280911-375-person2029" type="surname" value="HARRISON"></interp>
